{"tid":896923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東涌迫爆】東薈城超市貨架幾清空　區議員促限制經港珠澳大橋到港客量","createTime":"2018-11-10T12:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T12:08:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"057024cccfffdc66b39f8815c5fb51a767cf0740","tid":896923,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e8626a0e9e5ba90a27f129cdcdb34c66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe8626a0e9e5ba90a27f129cdcdb34c66.jpg&h=5dcd39cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋開通第三個周末，東涌今日下午依然迫滿人，不少旅客在區內超級市場掃貨。有區議員要求政府分流旅客到市區，又希望政府限制經港珠澳大橋到港的旅客數量。<br />\n<br />\n東薈城內的超級市場，今日成為旅客的掃貨熱點，奶粉、洗頭水及益力多等熱門商品都被搶購，收銀處前有旅客手上捧着5排益力多，貨架上洗頭水只剩數支。有銷售員表示，今個周末的情况已比上周輕微，經理亦有着她把貨物盡量推出貨架前方，看起來不像被清空。<br />\n<br />\n身兼立法會議員的民建聯離島區議員周浩鼎指，東涌今日仍人山人海，但秩序良好，期望政府加大力度，分流旅客至其他地區。他亦重申，把B6線巴士站搬離民居，是刻不容緩。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟荃灣區議員譚凱邦則不認同分流，指市區旅客本來已多，「大橋的問題要在大橋解決」，表示旅客多只為看大橋，大橋東人工島原亦有計劃設觀光位置，盼當局重啟計劃，讓旅客只在人工島參觀大橋，毋須到港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e871740cf95821bc7f8bfcee12026d37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe871740cf95821bc7f8bfcee12026d37.jpg&h=1b2866e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e86ffe230e7a185826879a135869f9ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe86ffe230e7a185826879a135869f9ef.jpg&h=5fea05c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e86eb88be5b105eda5787f7e9e83ab4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe86eb88be5b105eda5787f7e9e83ab4f.jpg&h=d26aba0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e86b94a8dfb7998327a88ae5c2e3867c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe86b94a8dfb7998327a88ae5c2e3867c.jpg&h=23160f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e86a4b9ca4388e75cd24487639d88612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe86a4b9ca4388e75cd24487639d88612.jpg&h=788373b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00001/1541853932129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2F1541853932129&d=oMbJSBbaPIxa%2BWjmUQq06aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8034ff26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2F1541853932129&h=448ec9ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00001/1541853932129</a>"},{"pid":"bdee4261f55387ae4a6ce73b837c03fb06c2e04b","tid":896923,"uid":17510,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"洗頭水都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5bbb80a5608277893562ee8acf122113a3e058","tid":896923,"uid":12021,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf910c797318de6feeb0026dd80418e07e9d6d3d","tid":896923,"uid":21279,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"未富先嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db31c4dd8feac0b4f22e3f804ec25c9969ddec1","tid":896923,"uid":23833,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"咁搞法物價一定升"},{"pid":"49f1a2575c109269efbe1de911f08b87f5960e9a","tid":896923,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"